            "id": 6085657,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 安可(AMKR-US)大跌5.05%，報22.73美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>安可(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMKR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMKR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMKR-US</a>)截至台北時間01日02:15股價下跌1.21美元，報22.73美元，跌幅5.05%，成交量1,775,278（股），盤中最高價23.88美元、最低價22.73美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.56%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.28%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.1%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-3.74%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>安可(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMKR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMKR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMKR-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+11.3%</li> <li>近 1 月：+14.05%</li> <li>近 3 月：+37.19%</li> <li>近 6 月：-3.74%</li> <li>今年以來：-6.81%</li></ul></section></main>",
